Text: Popsprd Migration Cc Popsprd bridge will be migrated to NahouScacl on April th for debugging purposes This migration should be transparent for Pops users with the exception of personal spread sheets using Pops tags The node name for Pops tags on personal spread sheets will need to be changed to NahouScacl to allow for updating of Pops data Please call me if you have any questions concerning the migration Steve
